      "name": "CFD hemolysis prediction vs. experimental RH index — 5 operating points",
      "description": "Simulation predictions of relative hemolysis index compared against experimental measurements at 5 flow-speed combinations. All predictions satisfy RH < 1 acceptance criterion. Mean absolute error 4.3%."
