    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index satisfy RH < 1 at all 5 operating points with maximum error 6.7%. The model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
